<p>When making the step from developer to management how far away from the code should you get?</p>

<p>The standard advice is 'stop coding' but Rands had an interesting blog post about how its important to keep coding.  </p>

<p><a href="http://www.randsinrepose.com/archives/2007/02/07/technicality.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.randsinrepose.com/archives/2007/02/07/technicality.html</a> </p>

<p>In my experience (working for a big telecomms company) its difficult if not impossible to keep coding.</p>
